{"tid":862891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又贏！中證監前首席顧問稱中美貿易戰對中國經濟影響不大","createTime":"2018-10-15T08:01:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T10:12:37.000Z","uid":41404,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"00b4b8df5cb0eb193f20457e61ef7075799c80a3","tid":862891,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T08:01:28.000Z","msg":"中國證監會昨日召開投資者座談會，聽取投資者對資本市場改革發展穩定的建議，中證監主席劉士余呼籲提振信心，又指正積極醞釀股市有關改革。<br />\n<br />\n中證監前首席顧問梁定邦表示，一直有進行股市改革，與投資者溝通很重要，不能讓短期情況影響市場信心。他指，近期市場波動，國際形勢對中國不利，尤其中美貿易戰，但他認為對中國經濟影響不大，只會造成心理影響。<br />\n<br />\n另外，本身亦是香港證監會前主席的梁定邦表示，港股是亞太區最有流通性的股市，市場一有少少恐慌或問題，港股就容易遭受沽壓，但他強調中港市場基本面並無大變化。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，近10-15年有很多細價股湧入香港，良莠不齊，認為證監會作出相關調查亦屬正常。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1423065-20181015.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1423065-20181015.htm&d=RE0JyUklRsIotNln4UT7XYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=f5d89319\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1423065-20181015.htm&h=603412a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1423065-20181015.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ca2f591314064aa9f7e7aa15f3580b6b4a01d4e8","tid":862891,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T08:16:34.000Z","msg":"沒事兒沒事兒 香港還有兩萬億外滙儲備"},{"pid":"d58484f1cfb720e0de6c5286404d6a456d6399cd","tid":862891,"uid":14497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T08:28:53.000Z","msg":"岩呀 唔打貿易戰中國都會自己收皮"},{"pid":"9f1f9cd0bdab2352d2f4344682f41dae31b030e0","tid":862891,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T09:11:36.000Z","msg":"外國商人都走曬 仲話影響唔大"},{"pid":"27f04080fe8698f8aa21f140b8907504058cc782","tid":862891,"uid":157138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T09:17:20.000Z","msg":"個咩劉士餘係大陸比人屌到飛起wor <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0bec22a2ffea9976b4be887c0a88a2da381af5f","tid":862891,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T09:18:46.000Z","msg":"影響不大，不過會支爆"},{"pid":"0134680552ff3abe2987d6b13fe10590379ce968","tid":862891,"uid":130177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T09:18:49.000Z","msg":"美國也有損失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3fa624f113b12660296df2540367d04270a384e","tid":862891,"uid":165012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T09:59:50.000Z","msg":"即係好多細價股都有問題"},{"pid":"841c490a599d13a0a8515996bdcc140db335605b","tid":862891,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:06:00.000Z","msg":"支那逼貴完劈價<br />\n樓市泡沫不攻自破<br />\n繼續掩耳盜鈴啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90521485b4375db9c10a81b69ebfeee8a956ea56","tid":862891,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:12:37.000Z","msg":"關稅只是美國自己傷害自己行為，中国根本冇影響，中或贏！"}]}